PRIVACY POLICY
Effective Date: 22/12/2023
Pine Games Teknoloji Anonim Şirketi
is a technology company specializing in the design and development of mobile games. 
                            This Privacy Policy aims to elucidate our practices regarding the gathering, storage, sharing, and usage of your personal
                            data, adhering to the legal standards of the countries in which we operate.
In this Policy, "personal data" encompasses all types of data or information that can be
                            used to identify, is connected to, describes, or is in any way associated with, either
                            directly or indirectly, a specific individual or household. This also includes any kind of
                            data or information considered as "personal data" or "personally identifiable information."
The scope of this Privacy Policy extends to a variety of platforms, including websites,
                            mobile applications, forums, blogs, and any offline services, as well as our marketing and
                            advertising endeavors across all platforms and other services that we may provide to you
                            from time to time (collectively, the "Services"). However, this Privacy Policy does not
                            pertain to individuals applying for jobs at Pine Games, current employees, or other staff
                            members.
This Privacy Policy applies to websites, mobile applications, forums, blogs, any offline
                            services, our marketing and advertising activities on all platforms This Privacy Policy does
                            not apply to Pine Games job applicants, employees, or other personnel.
Pine Games acts as the primary entity in control of your personal data collected in relation
                            to your usage of the Services. This role entails the responsibility and authority to
                            determine the usage of your personal data. According to this Privacy Policy, your personal
                            data will be processed to facilitate the Services when you download our mobile applications,
                            play our games, or engage with our Services in any form. Should you have concerns about the
                            provision of your data to us or its usage as outlined in this Privacy Policy, you are
                            encouraged to reach out to us. You can exercise your rights as detailed in the Security
                            section of this Privacy Policy.
Pine Games is the controller of the personal data we hold about you in connection with your
                            use of the Services. This means that we determine and are responsible for how your personal
                            data is used. Under this Privacy Policy, your personal data shall be processed in order to
                            provide the Services once you download our mobile applications, access and/or play our
                            games, or interact with our Services. If you have any other concerns about providing data to
                            us or it being used as described in this Privacy Policy, you may contact us and use your
                            rights explained under Security section of this Privacy Policy.
CONTACT US
