                                to provide and inform targeted advertising, as well as to provide advertising-related
                                services such as reporting, attribution, analytics and market research. Please see the
                                Third-Party Data Collection and Online Advertising section for more information.
With Your Consent:
We may disclose personal data about an individual to
                                certain other third parties or publicly with their consent or direction. For example,
                                with an individual's consent or direction, we may post their testimonial on our Sites or
                                service-related publications.
Sale of Assets and Change of Control:
If there is a sale of the assets
                                of Pine Games or corporate restructuring, or as a result of a change of control in the
                                shareholding structure of Pine Games, or in preparation for any of these events, any
                                third party to which Pine Games transfers or sells Pine Games' assets will have the
                                right to continue to use the personal and other information that you provide to us in
                                the manner set out in this Privacy Policy.
Legal Obligations and Rights:
We may disclose personal data to third
                                parties, such as legal advisors and law enforcement:
                                 in connection with the establishment, exercise, or defense of legal claims;
                                 to comply with laws or to respond to lawful requests and legal processes;
